response.headline: Korea's first pharmacy warehouse Mega Phactory offers Costco-style bulk skincare and OTC medicine at affordable prices
response.summary: Mega Phactory in Gyeonggi-do operates as Korea's first pharmacy warehouse, selling skincare and over-the-counter medications in bulk like Costco but without prescription drugs. The store offers Korean beauty products at significantly discounted prices compared to regular retail.

location_tags: Mega Phactory, 10 Godeung-ro 5-gil, Sujeong-gu, Seongnam-si, Gyeonggi-do

extracted_text: I knew I had to visit, and there was so much pharmacy skincare at even more affordable prices!!
They also have other OTC medicine and supplements, but no prescription medication (yet)!
I think it's worth a visit if you get a chance
image_details.key_interest: Korea's first pharmacy warehouse concept store for bulk skincare shopping
